MR. MEDVENE: Objection. Asked an answered.

THE COURT: Sustained.

MR. BAKER: Nothing further, Your Honor.

REDIRECT EXAMINATION BY MR. MEDVENE:

Q. Did anyone from the -- any representative of Mr. Simpson, call you
