A. No, sir.

Q. If they had, would you have spoken with them?

MR. BAKER: Calls for speculation.

THE COURT: Sustained.

Q. (BY MR. MEDVENE) If you assumed that Detectives Fuhrman and
Phillips arrived at Bundy at about 2:10 a.m., how much prior to that
