A. Yes.

Q. Or what appear to be -- what you believe were blood drops?

A. Yes.

Q. I ask that you mark, sir, what you believe were blood drops, in
that photograph.

MR. P. BAKER: What Exhibit is this?

MR. BLASIER: 162.

MR. P. BAKER: 162.

THE WITNESS: With this?

