<B>Additional Details:</B><BR>
<TEXTAREA NAME="QUESTION" ROWS="8" COLS="70"></TEXTAREA><P>

<P><B>You Must Read and Agree to the Following Terms in Order to Submit a Question:</B><BR>
<TT>The Legal Helpline is designed to provide interesting information, and make you a more informed consumer of legal services. The answers given here by our editors and panelists are intended as general discussions of law and education only and are not intended as legal advice. Because the Legal Helpline is an open discussion forum, your postings will not be confidential and you should not post the specific facts of your case, nor will the resulting discussions constitute the formation of a lawyer-client relationship.</TT></P>

<P><TT>Legal problems can be very serious and you should not rely on online legal discussions in making decisions about your own particular legal situation. Please consult your own attorney before making any decisions about your own legal matters. Accepting the terms of this disclaimer is a condition for visiting and/or using the Legal Helpline.</TT></P>

