grandma?"
A: I don't think quite the way you said it.  I may have referred to "these 
girls," speaking of the group as in general, when they get older--"They  ain't 
doing nothing now. What are they gonna do when  they get to be grandmas? 
I can see them when they're grandmas." Because I have said this many 
times: "I  can see them when they're grandmothers," even to  Nicole, 
