effect, yes. 
 
Q: And you were tired. Right? 
 
A: Oh, yes. 
 
Q: And you wanted to go home. Right? 
 
A: I wanted to see my kids. I wanted to go home. I wanted to--I 
don't know what I wanted to do. 
 
