MR. PETROCELLI: Romantically, emotionally, correct. 
 
THE WITNESS: Well, romantically. I don't know totally about 
emotionally. I was still concerned about her, yes. 
 
BY MR. PETROCELLI: 
Q: You didn't want to have a commitment with her anymore and a 
