A: To talk to my lawyers, I took notes, yes. 
 
Q: What happened after Puerto Rico to set you back with Nicole? 
 
A: Well, while I was in Puerto Rico, something was going on with 
Nicole. She was like-- she even said to me on two occasions she 
felt like she was having a nervous breakdown, but she couldn't 
explain why or what it was, and it was just--I would talk to her one 
