next day, she was somebody I didn't know. I expressed my concern 
to her mother while I was in Puerto Rico. I tried to get a hold of 
Cora, but she was going through her problems. I talked to Faye, 
who blamed it on Cora. 
And when I came home, I just--it was just something I did not 
want to have to deal with in my life. I just didn't want to deal with 
it anymore. 
 
