wedding. She left. I think Cora and Sydney was there, and Nicole 
just walked right out of the house and didn't even attend the 
wedding that night-- 
 
Q: Because Paula called? 
 
A: Because Paula called to wish Marcus and Katherine--wanted me 
to wish them a happy time. 
 
Q: From the time you start up this 1 relationship with Paula again 
